room_title: Escape room "American Revolution" by Portland Escape Rooms in Portland
room_address: 10700 SW Beaverton-Hillsdale Hwy Suite 100 Portland OR 97005
room_description: You and your friends have been charged with treason by the British Empire. They have locked you in a colonial room while they ready the firing squad for another Boston Massacre. An American sympathizer has left you clues to find the key and escape. You have 60 minutes to get out before the redcoats return!
